### Enter your solution:

```elixir
defmodule Tutorial.Profile do
  use Ash.Resource

  actions do
    defaults([:create])
  end

  attributes do
    uuid_primary_key(:id)
    attribute(:name, :string)
  end
end

defmodule Tutorial.Registry do
  use Ash.Registry

  # <--- Create your entries here
end

defmodule Tutorial do
  use Ash.Api

  # <--- Create your resources here
end
```

### Creating a Profile record

<!-- livebook:{"break_markdown":true} -->

We can now call `create!/1` to create a Profile.

```elixir
Tutorial.Profile
|> Ash.Changeset.for_create(:create, %{name: "My Name"})
|> Tutorial.create!()
```

